a\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Akbar\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"its own past successand\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"its hockey greats\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3482}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's administration\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you look at the overall picture, our seniors were celebrated but [they] did not evolve.\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the overall picture\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3582}, {\"ngram\": \"our seniors\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They continue to celebrate their past victories, not realising that the game has changed.\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their past victories\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3686}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no structure, no roadmap to progress, no professionalism,\\\" he told Al Jazeera from the Netherlands, where he runs a goalkeeping academy.\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3805, \"end\": 3815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2312865974460535e-15, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}, {\"begin\": 3825, \"end\": 3836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.489403285416287e-13, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no structure\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3750}, {\"ngram\": \"no roadmap\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3762}, {\"ngram\": \"no professionalism\", \"from\": 3776, \"to\": 3794}, {\"ngram\": \"a goalkeeping academy\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khwaja Junaid, a dashing midfielder from the 1980s and the 90s who won the best player award in the 1994 Champions Trophy, agrees.\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 4006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3876, \"end\": 3882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khawaja\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Khwaja\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khawaja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khawaja\"}, {\"begin\": 3981, \"end\": 3997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Champions_Trophy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.710411749153074e-27, \"text\": \"Champions Trophy\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Champions_Trophy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Champions_Trophy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dashing midfielder\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3911}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1980s\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3926}, {\"ngram\": \"the 90s\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 3938}, {\"ngram\": \"the best player award\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 3968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Junaid acknowledged the failure of Pakistan's top players when they became administrators.\", \"from\": 4008, \"to\": 4098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4043, \"end\": 4051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9853116176760273, \"rank\": 0.014907347137760136, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Junaid\", \"from\": 4008, \"to\": 4014}, {\"ngram\": \"the failure\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4039}, {\"ngram\": \"administrators\", \"from\": 4083, \"to\": 4097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said a robust system that ensures the development of the sport at the grassroots level no longer exists.\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a robust system\", \"from\": 4107, \"to\": 4122}, {\"ngram\": \"the development\", \"from\": 4136, \"to\": 4151}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4164}, {\"ngram\": \"the grassroots level\", \"from\": 4168, \"to\": 4188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Schools used to be the nurseries.\", \"from\": 4208, \"to\": 4242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schools\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4216}, {\"ngram\": \"the nurseries\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They would have interschool tournaments, then there were clubs where a talent was spotted.\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"interschool tournaments\", \"from\": 4259, \"to\": 4282}, {\"ngram\": \"clubs\", \"from\": 4300, \"to\": 4305}, {\"ngram\": \"a talent\", \"from\": 4312, \"to\": 4320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There used to be sports quota in colleges and universities, and players with potential were given scholarships,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports quota\", \"from\": 4351, \"to\": 4363}, {\"ngram\": \"colleges\", \"from\": 4367, \"to\": 4375}, {\"ngram\": \"universities\", \"from\": 4380, \"to\": 4392}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4405}, {\"ngram\": \"potential\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4420}, {\"ngram\": \"scholarships\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After academics, players had job opportunities at various organisations, both private and public, where they had set up sports departments.\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"academics\", \"from\": 4464, \"to\": 4473}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4482}, {\"ngram\": \"job opportunities\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4504}, {\"ngram\": \"various organisations\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4529}, {\"ngram\": \"sports departments\", \"from\": 4578, \"to\": 4596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a proper structure and players remained engaged with the game round the year,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a proper structure\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4626}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4638}, {\"ngram\": \"the game round\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the advent of the 90s saw the commercialisation of cricket, making its popularity soar over other sports.\", \"from\": 4698, \"to\": 4807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the advent\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4712}, {\"ngram\": \"the 90s\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 4723}, {\"ngram\": \"the commercialisation\", \"from\": 4728, \"to\": 4749}, {\"ngram\": \"cricket\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4760}, {\"ngram\": \"its popularity\", \"from\": 4769, \"to\": 4783}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports quotas were eliminated and vacant grounds were utilised for building residential units, depriving children of spaces to play.\", \"from\": 4808, \"to\": 4940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports quotas\", \"from\": 4808, \"to\": 4821}, {\"ngram\": \"vacant grounds\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"residential units\", \"from\": 4884, \"to\": 4901}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 4913, \"to\": 4921}, {\"ngram\": \"spaces\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 4931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Private schools mushroomed across the country on smaller properties with no facilities or encouragement for sports.\", \"from\": 4941, \"to\": 5056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Private schools\", \"from\": 4941, \"to\": 4956}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 4975, \"to\": 4986}, {\"ngram\": \"smaller properties\", \"from\": 4990, \"to\": 5008}, {\"ngram\": \"no facilities\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5027}, {\"ngram\": \"encouragement\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5044}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More recently, many public sector and government organisations which had some of the country's finest teams have shuttered their sports divisions, citing Pakistan's economic downturn.\", \"from\": 5058, \"to\": 5241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5212, \"end\": 5220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9853116176760273, \"rank\": 0.014907347137760136, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More recently, many public sector\", \"from\": 5058, \"to\": 5091}, {\"ngram\": \"government organisations\", \"from\": 5096, \"to\": 5120}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's finest teams\", \"from\": 5139, \"to\": 5165}, {\"ngram\": \"their sports divisions\", \"from\": 5181, \"to\": 5203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Pakistan underwent political upheaval after the end of an 11-year military dictatorship in 1988, hockey began to evolve globally.\", \"from\": 5243, \"to\": 5375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5246, \"end\": 5254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9853116176760273, \"rank\": 0.014907347137760136, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"political upheaval\", \"from\": 5265, \"to\": 5283}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5297}, {\"ngram\": \"an 11-year military dictatorship\", \"from\": 5301, \"to\": 5333}, {\"ngram\": \"hockey\", \"from\": 5343, \"to\": 5349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both the developments changed the country's fortunes.\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both the developments\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5397}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's fortunes\", \"from\": 5406, \"to\": 5428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Synthetic turf slowly replaced the grass grounds on which the game was traditionally played.\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Synthetic turf\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5445}, {\"ngram\": \"the grass grounds\", \"from\": 5462, \"to\": 5479}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 5489, \"to\": 5497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For a developing nation, it was an expensive change.\", \"from\": 5524, \"to\": 5576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a developing nation\", \"from\": 5528, \"to\": 5547}, {\"ngram\": \"an expensive change\", \"from\": 5556, \"to\": 5575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An average artificial turf today costs close to $500,000, with additional funds required for its maintenance.\", \"from\": 5577, \"to\": 5686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An average artificial turf\", \"from\": 5577, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"additional funds\", \"from\": 5640, \"to\": 5656}, {\"ngram\": \"its maintenance\", \"from\": 5670, \"to\": 5685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The change in surface also meant that other sports equipment had to change - and that too became costlier.\", \"from\": 5688, \"to\": 5794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The change\", \"from\": 5688, \"to\": 5698}, {\"ngram\": \"surface\", \"from\": 5702, \"to\": 5709}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports equipment\", \"from\": 5726, \"to\": 5748}, {\"ngram\": \"costlier\", \"from\": 5785, \"to\": 5793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, an ordinary hockey stick costs 6,000-8,000 rupees ($21-28), while a high-quality one is upwards of 20,000 rupees ($70).\", \"from\": 5795, \"to\": 5921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ordinary hockey stick\", \"from\": 5802, \"to\": 5826}, {\"ngram\": \"6,000-8,000 rupees\", \"from\": 5833, \"to\": 5851}, {\"ngram\": \"of 20,000 rupees\", \"from\": 5898, \"to\": 5914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly, a good quality hockey shoe suitable for synthetic turf costs 30,000-50,000 rupees ($107-180).\", \"from\": 5922, \"to\": 6026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good quality hockey shoe\", \"from\": 5933, \"to\": 5959}, {\"ngram\": \"synthetic turf\", \"from\": 5973, \"to\": 5987}, {\"ngram\": \"30,000-50,000 rupees\", \"from\": 5994, \"to\": 6014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This, in a country which, according to World Bank data, has a median income of 76,000 rupees ($266) per month.\", \"from\": 6027, \"to\": 6137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6066, \"end\": 6076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Bank\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.602035936108067e-18, \"text\": \"World Bank\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Bank\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Bank\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 6036, \"to\": 6045}, {\"ngram\": \"a median income\", \"from\": 6087, \"to\": 6102}, {\"ngram\": \"76,000 rupees\", \"from\": 6106, \"to\": 6119}, {\"ngram\": \"month\", \"from\": 6131, \"to\": 6136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oltmans said the change in playing surface affected Pakistan's performance and lamented a lack of effort by the authorities to keep up with the change.\", \"from\": 6139, \"to\": 6290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6191, \"end\": 6199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9853116176760273, \"rank\": 0.014907347137760136, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Oltmans\", \"from\": 6139, \"to\": 6146}, {\"ngram\": \"the change\", \"from\": 6152, \"to\": 6162}, {\"ngram\": \"surface\", \"from\": 6174, \"to\": 6181}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 6227, \"to\": 6233}, {\"ngram\": \"effort\", \"from\": 6237, \"to\": 6243}, {\"ngram\": \"the authorities\", \"from\": 6247, \"to\": 6262}, {\"ngram\": \"the change\", \"from\": 6279, \"to\": 6289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Junaid, who has also had multiple stints with the Pakistan team as coach and manager, agreed with the Dutch coach.\", \"from\": 6292, \"to\": 6406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6342, \"end\": 6350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9853116176760273, \"rank\": 0.014907347137760136, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 6394, \"end\": 6399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9989132517306489, \"rank\": 0.0010821229927515923, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Junaid\", \"from\": 6292, \"to\": 6298}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple stints\", \"from\": 6317, \"to\": 6332}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from\": 6359, \"to\": 6364}, {\"ngram\": \"manager\", \"from\": 6369, \"to\": 6376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He accused the Pakistan Hockey Federation (PHF), the government body tasked with promoting the sport in the country, of resting on past laurels instead of preparing for the future.\", \"from\": 6407, \"to\": 6587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6422, \"end\": 6454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pakistan Hockey Federation (PHF)\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the government body\", \"from\": 6456, \"to\": 6475}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 6498, \"to\": 6507}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 6511, \"to\": 6522}, {\"ngram\": \"past laurels\", \"from\": 6538, \"to\": 6550}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 6576, \"to\": 6586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We did not evolve and now we are in this almost interminable decline.\", \"from\": 6589, \"to\": 6659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this almost interminable decline\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Legacies continue when you have star players, [else] the game fades into oblivion.\\\"\", \"from\": 6660, \"to\": 6743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Legacies\", \"from\": 6660, \"to\": 6668}, {\"ngram\": \"star players\", \"from\": 6692, \"to\": 6704}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 6713, \"to\": 6721}, {\"ngram\": \"oblivion\", \"from\": 6733, \"to\": 6741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHF president Tariq Hussain Bugti told Al Jazeera the single biggest challenge the sporting body faces is a chronic lack of funds.\", \"from\": 6745, \"to\": 6875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6745, \"end\": 6748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.734315814959177e-34, \"text\": \"PHF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 6759, \"end\": 6772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tariq_Hussain\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.474479035956293e-26, \"text\": \"Tariq Hussain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tariq_Hussain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tariq_Hussain\"}, {\"begin\": 6773, \"end\": 6778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.758751370878835e-44, \"text\": \"Bugti\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\"}, {\"begin\": 6784, \"end\": 6794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2312865974460535e-15, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the single biggest challenge\", \"from\": 6795, \"to\": 6823}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting body\", \"from\": 6824, \"to\": 6841}, {\"ngram\": \"a chronic lack\", \"from\": 6851, \"to\": 6865}, {\"ngram\": \"funds\", \"from\": 6869, \"to\": 6874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have an annual budget of less than 4 million rupees [$14,350], whereas a single international tour for the national squad costs close to 30 million rupees [$100,000],\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 6877, \"to\": 7057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an annual budget\", \"from\": 6886, \"to\": 6902}, {\"ngram\": \"less than 4 million rupees\", \"from\": 6906, \"to\": 6932}, {\"ngram\": \"a single international tour\", \"from\": 6952, \"to\": 6979}, {\"ngram\": \"the national squad\", \"from\": 6984, \"to\": 7002}, {\"ngram\": \"close to 30 million rupees\", \"from\": 7009, \"to\": 7035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The board, Bugti says, only manages to support the team's travel with grants from the government.\", \"from\": 7059, \"to\": 7156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7070, \"end\": 7075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.758751370878835e-44, \"text\": \"Bugti\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The board\", \"from\": 7059, \"to\": 7068}, {\"ngram\": \"the team's travel\", \"from\": 7106, \"to\": 7123}, {\"ngram\": \"grants\", \"from\": 7129, \"to\": 7135}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 7141, \"to\": 7155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not have a league system.\", \"from\": 7158, \"to\": 7190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a league system\", \"from\": 7174, \"to\": 7189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not have our own stadium where players can practise, and we had to request the Pakistan Sports Board (PSB) to provide us a hockey stadium to hold training camps,\\\" he said, adding that the PHF lacks a marketing department to generate corporate sponsorship for the national team.\", \"from\": 7191, \"to\": 7474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7276, \"end\": 7297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Sports_Board\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pakistan Sports Board\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Sports_Board\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Sports_Board\"}, {\"begin\": 7299, \"end\": 7302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_broadcasting\", \"score\": 0.9999948263445869, \"rank\": 5.173682526848665e-06, \"text\": \"PSB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_broadcasting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_broadcasting\"}, {\"begin\": 7385, \"end\": 7388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.734315814959177e-34, \"text\": \"PHF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our own stadium\", \"from\": 7206, \"to\": 7221}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 7228, \"to\": 7235}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 7315, \"to\": 7317}, {\"ngram\": \"a hockey stadium\", \"from\": 7318, \"to\": 7334}, {\"ngram\": \"training camps\", \"from\": 7343, \"to\": 7357}, {\"ngram\": \"a marketing department\", \"from\": 7395, \"to\": 7417}, {\"ngram\": \"corporate sponsorship\", \"from\": 7430, \"to\": 7451}, {\"ngram\": \"the national team\", \"from\": 7456, \"to\": 7473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the PHF has also been battling its own set of problems, including allegations of financial mismanagement by administrators, who were already facing the heat for Pakistan's repeated failure to qualify for the Olympics and World Cups.\", \"from\": 7476, \"to\": 7719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7491, \"end\": 7494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.734315814959177e-34, \"text\": \"PHF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 7648, \"end\": 7656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9853116176760273, \"rank\": 0.014907347137760136, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7708, \"end\": 7718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5940669967865108e-14, \"text\": \"World Cups\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its own set\", \"from\": 7518, \"to\": 7529}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 7533, \"to\": 7541}, {\"ngram\": \"allegations\", \"from\": 7553, \"to\": 7564}, {\"ngram\": \"financial mismanagement\", \"from\": 7568, \"to\": 7591}, {\"ngram\": \"administrators\", \"from\": 7595, \"to\": 7609}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 7635, \"to\": 7643}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 7691, \"to\": 7703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In December, a battle for the PHF presidency saw a former president refusing to accept his removal and starting a parallel federation.\", \"from\": 7721, \"to\": 7855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7751, \"end\": 7754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.734315814959177e-34, \"text\": \"PHF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 7724, \"to\": 7732}, {\"ngram\": \"a battle\", \"from\": 7734, \"to\": 7742}, {\"ngram\": \"a former president\", \"from\": 7770, \"to\": 7788}, {\"ngram\": \"his removal\", \"from\": 7808, \"to\": 7819}, {\"ngram\": \"a parallel federation\", \"from\": 7833, \"to\": 7854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The current government resolved the matter after it came to power in February, merging the two bodies and declaring Bugti as the president of the PHF.\", \"from\": 7856, \"to\": 8006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7972, \"end\": 7977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.758751370878835e-44, \"text\": \"Bugti\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\"}, {\"begin\": 8002, \"end\": 8005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.734315814959177e-34, \"text\": \"PHF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Hockey_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The current government\", \"from\": 7856, \"to\": 7878}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 7888, \"to\": 7898}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 7916, \"to\": 7921}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 7925, \"to\": 7933}, {\"ngram\": \"the two bodies\", \"from\": 7943, \"to\": 7957}, {\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 7981, \"to\": 7994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bugti was in Oman when the Pakistani team lost to New Zealand and yet again failed to qualify for the Olympics, which officially begins in Paris on Friday.\", \"from\": 8008, \"to\": 8163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8008, \"end\": 8013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.758751370878835e-44, \"text\": \"Bugti\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bugti\"}, {\"begin\": 8021, \"end\": 8025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oman_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999942887715698, \"rank\": 5.70883460562946e-06, \"text\": \"Oman\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oman_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oman_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8035, \"end\": 8044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.864974145493912e-13, \"text\": \"Pakistani\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}, {\"begin\": 8058, \"end\": 8069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9993244168350013, \"rank\": 0.0005269637788216083, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8147, \"end\": 8152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.93179827086077e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 8106, \"to\": 8118}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 8156, \"to\": 8162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a national tragedy and it gave me an idea of the enormous task ahead,\\\" he told Al Jazeera.\", \"from\": 8164, \"to\": 8262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8251, \"end\": 8261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2312865974460535e-15, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a national tragedy\", \"from\": 8172, \"to\": 8190}, {\"ngram\": \"an idea\", \"from\": 8206, \"to\": 8213}, {\"ngram\": \"the enormous task\", \"from\": 8217, \"to\": 8234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knows the challenges.\", \"from\": 8264, \"to\": 8288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the challenges\", \"from\": 8273, \"to\": 8287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With almost non-existent grassroots competitions or domestic leagues, and no regular national or international events, Pakistani players, for most parts of the year, have little to look forward to.\", \"from\": 8289, \"to\": 8486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8408, \"end\": 8417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.864974145493912e-13, \"text\": \"Pakistani\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"almost non-existent grassroots competitions\", \"from\": 8294, \"to\": 8337}, {\"ngram\": \"domestic leagues\", \"from\": 8341, \"to\": 8357}, {\"ngram\": \"no regular national or international events\", \"from\": 8363, \"to\": 8406}, {\"ngram\": \"most parts\", \"from\": 8431, \"to\": 8441}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 8445, \"to\": 8453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ashraf, one of the country's rising stars, made his debut in 2019.\", \"from\": 8488, \"to\": 8554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ashraf\", \"from\": 8488, \"to\": 8494}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's rising stars\", \"from\": 8503, \"to\": 8529}, {\"ngram\": \"his debut\", \"from\": 8536, \"to\": 8545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the five years since, the ace centre-forward has played for the national team in just 59 matches, scoring 29 goals.\", \"from\": 8555, \"to\": 8673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the five years\", \"from\": 8558, \"to\": 8572}, {\"ngram\": \"the national team\", \"from\": 8618, \"to\": 8635}, {\"ngram\": \"just 59 matches\", \"from\": 8639, \"to\": 8654}, {\"ngram\": \"29 goals\", \"from\": 8664, \"to\": 8672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By comparison, Sohail Abbas, Pakistan's greatest goal scorer and one of the finest drag-flick pushers in the history of the game, played 311 matches between 1998 and 2012, averaging 22 games a year.\", \"from\": 8674, \"to\": 8872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8689, \"end\": 8701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sohail_Abbas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sohail Abbas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sohail_Abbas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sohail_Abbas\"}, {\"begin\": 8703, \"end\": 8711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9853116176760273, \"rank\": 0.014907347137760136, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comparison\", \"from\": 8677, \"to\": 8687}, {\"ngram\": \"the finest drag-flick pushers\", \"from\": 8746, \"to\": 8775}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 8779, \"to\": 8790}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 8794, \"to\": 8802}, {\"ngram\": \"311 matches\", \"from\": 8811, \"to\": 8822}, {\"ngram\": \"22 games\", \"from\": 8856, \"to\": 8864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the Nations Cup tournament in Poland in June, Ashraf, 24, has been home in Sargodha, a city in Pakistan's Punjab province, training on his own.\", \"from\": 8874, \"to\": 9023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8910, \"end\": 8916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9588249579351764e-15, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8955, \"end\": 8963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sargodha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1854447701848413e-19, \"text\": \"Sargodha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sargodha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sargodha\"}, {\"begin\": 8975, \"end\": 8983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9853116176760273, \"rank\": 0.014907347137760136, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8986, \"end\": 8992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punjab\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.746123527784704e-12, \"text\": \"Punjab\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punjab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punjab\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Nations Cup tournament\", \"from\": 8880, \"to\": 8906}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 8920, \"to\": 8924}, {\"ngram\": \"Ashraf\", \"from\": 8926, \"to\": 8932}, {\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 8965, \"to\": 8971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Asian Champions Trophy will be held in China in September and the national team has not begun its practice camp yet.\", \"from\": 9025, \"to\": 9145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9035, \"end\": 9051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Champions_Trophy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.710411749153074e-27, \"text\": \"Champions Trophy\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Champions_Trophy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Champions_Trophy\"}, {\"begin\": 9068, \"end\": 9073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999996131510509, \"rank\": 3.868461253694883e-07, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 9077, \"to\": 9086}, {\"ngram\": \"the national team\", \"from\": 9091, \"to\": 9108}, {\"ngram\": \"its practice camp\", \"from\": 9123, \"to\": 9140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ashraf said it was an example of one of the challenges before the PHF: to eliminate uncertainty over the squad.\", \"from\": 9146, \"to\": 9257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ashraf\", \"from\": 9146, \"to\": 9152}, {\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 9165, \"to\": 9175}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenges\", \"from\": 9186, \"to\": 9200}, {\"ngram\": \"the PHF\", \"from\": 9208, \"to\": 9215}, {\"ngram\": \"uncertainty\", \"from\": 9230, \"to\": 9241}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 9247, \"to\": 9256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have three months before our next tournament, but we do not have a coach, we do not have a ground to play on, we do not have a camp yet.\", \"from\": 9259, \"to\": 9399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our next tournament\", \"from\": 9288, \"to\": 9307}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 9328, \"to\": 9335}, {\"ngram\": \"a ground\", \"from\": 9352, \"to\": 9360}, {\"ngram\": \"a camp\", \"from\": 9388, \"to\": 9394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just try to keep myself fit by training three times a day,\\\" Ashraf told Al Jazeera.\", \"from\": 9400, \"to\": 9485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9474, \"end\": 9484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2312865974460535e-15, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ashraf\", \"from\": 9462, \"to\": 9468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need matches.\", \"from\": 9487, \"to\": 9504, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 9496, \"to\": 9503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need a domestic league to play,\\\" he insisted.\", \"from\": 9505, \"to\": 9553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a domestic league\", \"from\": 9513, \"to\": 9530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His teammate, Sufyan Khan, known for his slick penalty corners, echoed the sentiments.\", \"from\": 9555, \"to\": 9641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9576, \"end\": 9580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\", \"score\": 0.9784735910580313, \"rank\": 0.021999989717721012, \"text\": \"Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q33999\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His teammate\", \"from\": 9555, \"to\": 9567}, {\"ngram\": \"his slick penalty corners\", \"from\": 9592, \"to\": 9617}, {\"ngram\": \"the sentiments\", \"from\": 9626, \"to\": 9640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old from Bannu city in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa province said the players ne